data.description: A  beautiful bay view from the contemporary home that has many outstanding features. Australian  cypress flooring hickory cabinets in the spacious kitchen and  solid fir beams to mention a few. The over sized 3 car garage 24x38 has a full apartment or mother in law cottage above with its own bath and kitchen, Enjoy privacy in the park like setting on 8 plus acres,  The outside decks are mahogany and there is a large patio for entertaining guests, There 3 master bedrooms all with their own bath and walk in closet plus a den hall half bath and large mud room for the washer and dryer. This home was built with the best materials such as anderson wood windows and doors. This a real 1 of kind property.
